TopicTitle: I have no smoke coming out my b9 aerospace engines

Articles.Content: Does anyone have any suggestions on why this is happening? I know it's not a huge deal as the parts still work, but it would be a bit better than the pathetic glow on the nozzle of cf34 turbofans that doesn't show there's actually any exhaust. I've still got afterburning effects and the flames coming out sabres, and my stock and kw rocketry stuff works perfectly. Does anyone know what I can do to fix this?
